Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮你改变你的着装\N{\fs28}I can help you change your outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有你自己可以改变你的内心\N{\fs28}but only you can change yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要问的问题就是\N{\fs28}The question you have to ask is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想要继续像以前那样墨守陈规的平平淡淡过一辈子\N{\fs28}do you want to hold onto the way things used to be and be right,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是想要打破常规 开开心心过一辈子\N{\fs28}or do you want to change and be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还认为我是弯的吗\N{\fs28}You still think I'm gay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老娘不在乎了\N{\fs28}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我一直在考虑我们宝宝\N{\fs28}So, I have been thinking about the outfit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在庆生会的时候穿什么样的衣服\N{\fs28}our baby will wear for the birth announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 亲爱的 我真不想就这件事小题大做\N{\fs28}Oh, sweetie, I really don't want this to be a whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他想穿什么就穿什么\N{\fs28}So he can wear whatever you want him to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么让你改变主意了\N{\fs28}What made you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个坑爹的晚宴\N{\fs28}That silly dinner party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 我又像是回到了高中一样\N{\fs28}Last night, I became that kid from junior high all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样评判别人 因为害怕被别人评判\N{\fs28}Judging someone because I was afraid of being judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只有你这样\N{\fs28}It wasn't just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shania也是这样\N{\fs28}It was Shania, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们不打破成规 没有发展的眼光 我们就会挂掉\N{\fs28}If we don't change, if we don't evolve, then we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有再看到有兽脚亚目食肉恐龙在这周围了\N{\fs28}You don't see any theropod dinosaurs hanging around
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 你想知道原因吗\N{\fs28}anymore, do you? You want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为驰龙科恐龙\N{\fs28}Because dromaeosauridae...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 天啊 David 你这样就是要我\N{\fs28}Oh, my God, David, it's like you want me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别注意听你说话\N{\fs28}to stop paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想我们的儿子\N{\fs28}I just don't want our son
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我这样成长\N{\fs28}to grow up the way that I did:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惧怕做自己\N{\fs28}Afraid to be myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直打安全牌 这样就不会被别人指手画脚\N{\fs28}playing into stereotypes so he won't be judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有我不惧怕了 他才能够做到\N{\fs28}But he can only do that if I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 继续吧\N{\fs28}So, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们儿子穿上裙子 长袍\N{\fs28}Put our son in the dress... gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的确有一个很小的调整\N{\fs28}But I do have one slight adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就完美了\N{\fs28}It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭配很古怪 很惊艳 还会让所有人困惑\N{\fs28}It's odd and amazing, and it will confuse everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱死这搭配了\N{\fs28}And I love it.
